  "text": "it is straightforward to check that equations (2) hold. When q < 13, Remark 4.4 shows that the above conditions on b 0 , a 1 , a 2 are still sufficient for x 3 + a 2 x 2 + a 1 x x 2 + x + b 0 to be permutation. A direct check with Magma [CITATION_1] shows that they are also necessary. Proof.",
